    pair_with_planet: 'Pluto — the planet of *cosmic-fate*, of the *underworld-trickster*, of the *unpredictable cosmic-power* that *plays kings and beggars equally*; Tezcatlipoca is the Mexica Pluto in its most-concentrated form.',
    pair_with_planet_slug: 'pluto',
